		<h3>Sonnax Products Named Tops for 2011 <em class="date">3/7/11</em></h3>
		<p>Thank you to the readers of <em>Transmission Digest</em> for voting four Sonnax parts Top Ten Shop Products of 2011! Our winners were the 4R70W valve body retaining plate, Chrysler RFE line pressure booster kits, 46/47 RH/RE 2nd gear super hold servo and our dual seal billet accumulator piston kit. Entries were featured in the October 2010 magazine issue, with the winners announced in March 2011. Many will be on display at <a href="http://www.showpowerexpo.com/">Showpower Expo 2011</a>, March 17-19 in Indianapolis, Ind. <%= link_to 'Learn More&hellip;', news_3_7_11_path %></p>

